org.neo4j.driver.v1

Interface Record

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MapAccessorWithDefaultValue

    @Immutable
public interface Record
extends MapAccessorWithDefaultValue
    Container for Cypher result values.

    Streams of records are returned from Cypher statement execution, contained within a StatementResult.

    A record is a form of ordered map and, as such, contained values can be accessed by either positional index or textual key.

    Since:
    1.0
